block main
  .block-text.intro
    p
      | Are you an incoming freshman who wants to find out more about the school? 
      | Or do you simply want to make some friends and have fun?
    p
      | NUS Computing Freshmen Orientation Projects (FOP) 2017 presents to you: 
      strong Tempus Nova
      | . With an exciting lineup of events, we will help integrate into our
      | Computing family in no time. At FOP, not only do you get the opportunity to meet 
      | other incoming freshmen, you will also meet seniors who can provide valuable advice 
      | to follow you through your University years. Join us this summer for the best 
      | freshmen experience youâ€™ll ever have!

